{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T09:04:05.850Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Dynamic task decomposition and adaptive re-planning"},{"type":"text","text":" in hierarchical agent architectures means the orchestrator "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"doesn’t just break a goal into fixed subtasks once"},{"type":"text","text":"; it "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"iteratively decomposes, executes, monitors, and re-plans"},{"type":"text","text":" as the world changes, tools fail, or new information arrives. Instead of a rigid, one-shot plan, the agent maintains a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tree or graph of subgoals"},{"type":"text","text":" and updates it dynamically, adding new subtasks, removing failed ones, or reordering dependencies as needed."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dynamic decomposition is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"adaptive partitioning"},{"type":"text","text":" of complex objectives into context-sensitive subtasks using "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"execution feedback"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adaptive re-planning is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"ongoing cycle"},{"type":"text","text":" of:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Running the current subtask.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Monitoring"},{"type":"text","text":": Watching for errors, delays, or missing data.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluation"},{"type":"text","text":": Checking if the result matches expectations.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-planning"},{"type":"text","text":": Updating the plan when something goes wrong or new info arrives."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is not just error recovery; it’s "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continuous plan refinement"},{"type":"text","text":" as circumstances change."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Single-shot planning fails on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"long-horizon, multimodal tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" that require multi-step reasoning and perception. LLMs struggle with:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-term coordination"},{"type":"text","text":" between planning and execution.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Inefficiency of indiscriminate tool use"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., calling vision APIs unnecessarily).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Context changes"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., a website changes structure, an API returns different data)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dynamic decomposition and adaptive re-planning solve this by:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Breaking tasks into manageable subgoals"},{"type":"text","text":" that can be validated independently.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Using feedback to refine the plan"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., if a scraper fails, decompose into “inspect HTML → adjust selector → retry”).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Supporting selective tool invocation"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., only call vision when needed).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Handling dependencies and coherence"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., analysis depends on scraped data)."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of the plan as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"living tree"},{"type":"text","text":" that grows and shrinks:\n- You start with a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"root goal"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., “analyze market trends”).\n- The agent "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"decomposes"},{"type":"text","text":" it into subgoals (e.g., “scrape → analyze → write”).\n- As subgoals execute, the agent "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"monitors"},{"type":"text","text":" for failures or surprises.\n- If something fails, the agent "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"re-plans"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., “scrape failed → decompose into ‘inspect HTML → fix selector → retry scrape’”).\n- The tree "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"updates dynamically"},{"type":"text","text":" as new subgoals are added or removed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"recursive two-stage planner-executor architecture"},{"type":"text","text":" that enables continuous task refinement and adaptation."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Dynamic decomposition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The orchestrator uses a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hierarchical Task DAG (HTDAG)"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tree structure"},{"type":"text","text":" to decompose high-level objectives into subtasks while maintaining dependencies."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Initial decomposition\ngoal = \"Analyze market trends for AI startup pricing\"\nsubgoals = {\n    \"scrape\": {\"task\": \"scrape\", \"deps\": []},\n    \"analyze\": {\"task\": \"analyze\", \"deps\": [\"scrape\"]},\n    \"write\": {\"task\": \"write\", \"deps\": [\"analyze\"]}\n}"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The HTDAG maintains the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dependency graph"},{"type":"text","text":" so the orchestrator knows which subtasks can run in parallel and which must wait."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Iterative execution and monitoring"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The orchestrator executes subtasks one by one (or in parallel if independent), monitoring for:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Errors"},{"type":"text","text":": Tool failures, API errors, network issues.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Missing data"},{"type":"text","text":": Scraped data is empty, analysis results are incomplete.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Surprises"},{"type":"text","text":": Website structure changed, API returned unexpected fields."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"for subgoal in execute_order(subgoals):  # respects dependencies\n    result = execute_subtask(subgoal)\n    if result.error:\n        handle_error(subgoal, result.error)\n    else:\n        update_state(subgoal, result)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Adaptive re-planning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When a subtask fails or surprises occur, the orchestrator "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"re-plans"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add new subtasks"},{"type":"text","text":": “scrape failed → add ‘inspect HTML’ and ‘fix selector’.”\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Remove failed subtasks"},{"type":"text","text":": “analysis is impossible → skip and use fallback.”\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reorder dependencies"},{"type":"text","text":": “write can start earlier if analysis is partial.”\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Change strategy"},{"type":"text","text":": “use a different scraper or API.”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"def handle_error(subgoal, error):\n    if subgoal.task == \"scrape\" and error == \"selector_not_found\":\n        # Re-plan: decompose into inspect → fix → retry\n        new_subgoals = {\n            \"inspect\": {\"task\": \"inspect_html\", \"deps\": []},\n            \"fix_selector\": {\"task\": \"fix_selector\", \"deps\": [\"inspect\"]},\n            \"retry_scrape\": {\"task\": \"scrape\", \"deps\": [\"fix_selector\"]}\n        }\n        update_dag(new_subgoals)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"DEPART"},{"type":"text","text":" framework’s loop: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Divide → Evaluate → Plan → Act → Reflect → Track"},{"type":"text","text":", supporting dynamic task decomposition and feedback-driven control."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. Continuous refinement"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The agent doesn’t just re-plan once; it "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continuously refines"},{"type":"text","text":" the plan as more feedback arrives. This is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"recursive two-stage planner-executor"},{"type":"text","text":" pattern: the planner refines the plan, the executor runs it, feedback goes back to the planner, and the plan is updated again."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementation patterns"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ReAcTree: Tree-based hierarchical planning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ReAcTree automatically decomposes complex tasks into a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tree of subgoals"},{"type":"text","text":" where:\n- Each node is a subgoal.\n- Children are sub-subgoals.\n- The agent executes the tree recursively, backtracking and re-planning when nodes fail."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Tree structure\nroot = {\n    \"goal\": \"Analyze market trends\",\n    \"children\": [\n        {\"goal\": \"Scrape pricing data\", \"children\": []},\n        {\"goal\": \"Analyze trends\", \"children\": []},\n        {\"goal\": \"Write report\", \"children\": []}\n    ]\n}"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If “Scrape pricing data” fails, the agent backtracks and adds a new subtree: “Inspect HTML → Fix selector → Retry scrape.”"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"DEPART: Divide-Evaluate-Plan-Act-Reflect-Track"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DEPART uses a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"three-agent hierarchy"},{"type":"text","text":" (planner, perception, execution) that collaborates through the loop:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Divide"},{"type":"text","text":": Planner breaks the goal into subtasks.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluate"},{"type":"text","text":": Perception evaluates if subtasks need vision or other tools.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Plan"},{"type":"text","text":": Planner creates a detailed plan.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Act"},{"type":"text","text":": Execution runs the plan.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reflect"},{"type":"text","text":": Agent evaluates results and feeds back to planner.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track"},{"type":"text","text":": System tracks state and updates the plan."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This loop supports "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dynamic task decomposition"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"selective vision invocation"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"AgentOrchestra: Two-tier planning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AgentOrchestra uses a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"top-level planning agent"},{"type":"text","text":" that decomposes tasks and coordinates "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"modular sub-agents"},{"type":"text","text":" responsible for execution."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The planner:\n- Decomposes high-level goals into subgoals.\n- Assigns subgoals to sub-agents.\n- Monitors execution and re-plans when needed."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Handles complex, multi-phase tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" that single-shot planning cannot."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Adapts to changing circumstances"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., website changes, API errors)."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduces hallucination"},{"type":"text","text":" by validating subgoals independently."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improves efficiency"},{"type":"text","text":" by using tools selectively (e.g., vision only when needed)."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Maintains coherence"},{"type":"text","text":" across dependencies (e.g., analysis depends on scraped data)."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-offs"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Robust on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"long-horizon tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" with multi-step reasoning.\n- Adapts to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dynamic environments"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., changing APIs, websites).\n- Reduces "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tool waste"},{"type":"text","text":" by using tools selectively."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Trade-offs:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- More "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"complex"},{"type":"text","text":" to implement (planner, executor, feedback loop).\n- Requires "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"state tracking"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"dependency management"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- Can introduce "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"latency"},{"type":"text","text":" if re-planning is frequent.\n- Requires "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"monitoring logic"},{"type":"text","text":" for errors and surprises."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dynamic decomposition "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"adapts task partitioning"},{"type":"text","text":" based on execution feedback, not just initial planning."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adaptive re-planning is an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"ongoing cycle"},{"type":"text","text":" of execution, monitoring, evaluation, and re-planning."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The plan is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"living tree or DAG"},{"type":"text","text":" that grows and shrinks as subgoals succeed or fail."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This pattern is critical for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"long-horizon, multimodal tasks"},{"type":"text","text":" that require multi-step reasoning and perception."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hierarchical agents (planner, perception, execution) collaborate through loops like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Divide-Evaluate-Plan-Act-Reflect-Track"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
